794
01:38:53,542 --> 01:38:56,300
Don't look at me.

795
01:39:06,036 --> 01:39:09,669
Nurse!
Call doctor!

796
01:39:14,708 --> 01:39:16,567
Atsumi?
It's me.

797
01:39:17,622 --> 01:39:20,559
Hiroko just fell off the bed.

798
01:39:20,661 --> 01:39:21,411
What do you mean?

799
01:39:23,122 --> 01:39:26,309
She kind of rolled over like she did it on purpose.

800
01:39:29,051 --> 01:39:31,247
The doctor says it's nothing.

801
01:39:31,895 --> 01:39:33,833
I'll be right there.

802
01:39:34,442 --> 01:39:35,192
Come here soon.

803
01:39:36,403 --> 01:39:39,919
Don't come near her anymore.

804
01:39:40,887 --> 01:39:45,309
Leave her alone.
There's nothing more to do for Hiroko.

805
01:39:46,708 --> 01:39:47,372
Ok?

806
01:39:48,387 --> 01:39:48,864
Yes.

807
01:40:23,650 --> 01:40:24,556
Get the ferry?

808
01:40:24,837 --> 01:40:25,814
Later is fine.

809
01:40:29,212 --> 01:40:31,868
I heard you turned down Hirono-san.

810
01:40:33,681 --> 01:40:35,689
You don't have to worry about that.

811
01:40:38,134 --> 01:40:39,126
I know.

812
01:40:41,259 --> 01:40:44,736
My uncle hasn't spoken to me since then.

813
01:40:45,986 --> 01:40:49,954
Nobody is on my side anymore.

814
01:40:50,197 --> 01:40:52,697
Can you be patient with me for a little while longer?

815
01:40:54,150 --> 01:40:56,837
I have a lot of important things on my mind right now.

816
01:40:57,439 --> 01:41:03,532
But I don't want to cause Hiroko any more pain.

817
01:41:04,056 --> 01:41:07,868
There's also Shota.
Can't you wait a little longer?

818
01:41:14,429 --> 01:41:15,382
I have to go.

819
01:41:17,898 --> 01:41:20,718
I can't run away.

820
01:41:40,316 --> 01:41:41,581
Are you going out?

821
01:41:44,042 --> 01:41:45,605
Of course.

822
01:41:59,222 --> 01:42:04,097
You dragged Hiroko off the bed.

823
01:42:05,401 --> 01:42:06,292
Mother.

824
01:42:07,284 --> 01:42:12,690
That's why Hiroko has to stay in the hospital for two more weeks.

825
01:42:16,034 --> 01:42:20,549
Your uncle talks bad about you.

826
01:42:23,448 --> 01:42:28,940
I should've left you at Echigo-Yuzawa.

827
01:42:45,847 --> 01:42:52,416
This is a truly slanderous letter.

828
01:42:53,104 --> 01:42:55,932
Thank you for letting me know.

829
01:42:57,167 --> 01:43:00,292
This is really bad.

830
01:43:00,807 --> 01:43:04,143
This is full of malice.

831
01:43:04,862 --> 01:43:07,838
You don't need to worry about this letter.

832
01:43:09,096 --> 01:43:11,276
But you always get this kind of letters.

833
01:43:11,377 --> 01:43:15,198
I couldn't just ignore it, could I?

834
01:43:21,233 --> 01:43:22,929
I'm so embarrassed.

835
01:43:35,582 --> 01:43:36,856
What can I do for you?

836
01:43:38,348 --> 01:43:40,434
Nothing.

837
01:43:42,278 --> 01:43:46,286
You can leave now.

838
01:43:47,215 --> 01:43:51,153
Don't worry.
I have permission from the school.

839
01:43:53,129 --> 01:43:56,661
Shota... I've been asked to keep him at uncle's house.

840
01:43:58,887 --> 01:44:01,262
It's easier for me too.

841
01:44:02,856 --> 01:44:05,348
I don't want you to worry about me.

842
01:44:06,715 --> 01:44:08,590
I'm sure everything will be fine now.

843
01:44:11,536 --> 01:44:13,793
I feel sorry.

844
01:44:16,043 --> 01:44:17,473
You feel sorry?

845
01:44:19,309 --> 01:44:20,614
I don't want you to say that.

846
01:44:28,293 --> 01:44:29,160
Hiroko?

847
01:44:29,645 --> 01:44:34,715
If you're going to talk like that.
I don't want you here.

848
01:44:36,950 --> 01:44:39,114
I don't want you here.

849
01:44:42,762 --> 01:44:44,418
I don't want you to stay.

850
01:45:04,498 --> 01:45:05,287
Come in.

851
01:45:08,849 --> 01:45:11,006
I apologize for any inconvenience caused.

852
01:45:12,795 --> 01:45:14,334
Have a seat.

853
01:45:16,607 --> 01:45:19,779
I have something to talk to you about.

854
01:45:22,099 --> 01:45:23,779
How's your wife?

855
01:45:24,537 --> 01:45:27,318
Her shoulder's better now.
The cast is still in place.

856
01:45:28,701 --> 01:45:32,576
She just twisted her neck a little bit, so she's got tingling in her arms and legs.

857
01:45:33,467 --> 01:45:35,490
How about her face?

858
01:45:35,615 --> 01:45:38,412
She got a little cut above her eye, but she'll be fine.

859
01:45:39,076 --> 01:45:40,076
Will it leave a scar?

860
01:45:40,412 --> 01:45:41,295
I think she'll be fine.

861
01:45:41,881 --> 01:45:44,592
I'm worried about your wife.

862
01:45:48,302 --> 01:45:51,717
By the way, did you just build a house over here?

863
01:45:53,326 --> 01:45:53,724
Yes.

864
01:45:54,138 --> 01:45:56,904
Then I guess it's hard for you to transfer.

865
01:45:57,521 --> 01:45:58,521
Is that what you're telling me now?

866
01:45:59,138 --> 01:46:00,795
Don't be so hard on yourself.

867
01:46:01,295 --> 01:46:03,185
I've talked it over with Take.

868
01:46:03,210 --> 01:46:04,240
My father?

869
01:46:07,154 --> 01:46:09,842
I got this letter.

870
01:46:11,708 --> 01:46:12,544
This.

871
01:46:13,709 --> 01:46:16,256
It's a small island here.

872
01:46:17,240 --> 01:46:20,342
There's nothing more interesting than rumors about a man and a woman.
You want to read it?

873
01:46:23,383 --> 01:46:24,781
No thanks.

874
01:46:25,422 --> 01:46:30,836
Your wife and Take's niece had an argument in Sakyobana.

875
01:46:31,437 --> 01:46:34,937
I heard your wife was almost pushed off a cliff.

876
01:46:36,391 --> 01:46:41,250
I don't think that's true.
Do you think this letter speaks for your wife?

877
01:47:30,370 --> 01:47:32,245
I'm off.

878
01:48:07,532 --> 01:48:09,212
Thank you for the food.

879
01:48:16,720 --> 01:48:17,775
Sit there.

880
01:48:25,704 --> 01:48:27,743
Hiroko will be released from the hospital soon.

881
01:48:29,282 --> 01:48:34,743
I'm going to take care of her and Shota.

882
01:48:40,580 --> 01:48:44,041
Even with you here, I think this is a big house.

883
01:48:45,595 --> 01:48:49,033
But I think it would be difficult for you and her to live together.

884
01:48:51,220 --> 01:48:54,306
Hiroko is suffering and so are you.

885
01:48:59,408 --> 01:49:00,595
I don't tell the reason

886
01:49:02,330 --> 01:49:05,705
I think you understand that very well.

887
01:49:06,931 --> 01:49:09,963
Please apologize to him.

888
01:49:11,150 --> 01:49:13,611
You brought this all on yourself.

889
01:49:13,636 --> 01:49:14,728
Shut up!

890
01:49:17,402 --> 01:49:20,160
I'm not emotional.

891
01:49:23,074 --> 01:49:25,293
It's up to you.

892
01:49:26,863 --> 01:49:30,012
Think about it, please.

893
01:49:33,504 --> 01:49:35,910
I'm leaving today.

894
01:49:37,332 --> 01:49:40,918
No, I don't mean today or tomorrow.

895
01:49:42,067 --> 01:49:44,918
Think about it, please.

896
01:49:46,684 --> 01:49:48,699
But I'm leaving today.

897
01:49:49,793 --> 01:49:51,770
You can have her back anytime.

898
01:49:54,629 --> 01:49:57,465
I don't have anywhere to go, but I'll be fine.

899
01:49:59,011 --> 01:50:03,191
But my mother doesn't mind if she stay here, does she?

900
01:50:03,527 --> 01:50:05,160
That's a given.

901
01:50:05,910 --> 01:50:08,660
You don't need to worry about her.

902
01:50:09,848 --> 01:50:12,199
It's not worth it for you to say that.

903
01:50:16,881 --> 01:50:19,849
If I fail, I'll come back somehow.

904
01:50:21,295 --> 01:50:34,896
But your heart is so polluted that I don't think you'll ever be able to recover.

905
01:51:01,418 --> 01:51:04,191
Are you really leaving out today?

906
01:51:05,535 --> 01:51:06,855
Because we made a promise.

907
01:51:08,683 --> 01:51:10,777
It's starting to rain.

908
01:51:11,121 --> 01:51:12,418
Are you alright?

909
01:51:12,443 --> 01:51:13,683
I'm alright.

910
01:51:15,191 --> 01:51:18,738
I'm not alright.

911
01:51:22,418 --> 01:51:24,473
I feel pain.

912
01:51:26,504 --> 01:51:33,918
I want you to be happy more than anyone else.

913
01:52:45,364 --> 01:52:48,794
She is not good at greeting.

914
01:52:51,067 --> 01:52:57,302
I will greet you on her behalf.
Thank you for all your help.

915
01:53:00,192 --> 01:53:01,130
Tomoe.

916
01:53:04,239 --> 01:53:11,809
Do you want to go with her?

917
01:53:14,323 --> 01:53:15,590
Tell me.

918
01:53:21,275 --> 01:53:25,213
To be honest, it's 50-50.

919
01:53:27,018 --> 01:53:32,736
If Hiroko comes back, I won't be needed in this house.

920
01:53:34,291 --> 01:53:35,064
So.

921
01:53:35,893 --> 01:53:37,228
Stop it....

922
01:53:38,807 --> 01:53:44,486
And if you go with them, you will perish, too.

923
01:53:47,705 --> 01:53:51,525
Only she can go to hell.

924
01:53:53,166 --> 01:53:53,963
Bros.

925
01:54:00,045 --> 01:54:06,170
My heart is gone too.

926
01:54:08,842 --> 01:54:18,654
People who are related to me thought I could change.

927
01:54:20,431 --> 01:54:22,962
But I couldn't do that.

928
01:54:27,454 --> 01:54:35,407
I am a really terrible teacher.

929
01:54:37,381 --> 01:54:39,413
I feel bad.

930
01:55:36,092 --> 01:55:36,874
What's wrong?

931
01:55:37,061 --> 01:55:39,647
I'm sorry.
I left the house.

932
01:55:39,836 --> 01:55:40,923
Come in.

933
01:55:42,426 --> 01:55:45,246
I just brought some personal stuff with me for now.

934
01:55:46,028 --> 01:55:46,895
You have nothing.

935
01:55:47,439 --> 01:55:48,845
I left it at the inn.

936
01:55:49,266 --> 01:55:49,746
Inn?

937
01:55:56,970 --> 01:55:58,544
I'm evil.

938
01:56:00,004 --> 01:56:01,557
For you and Hiroko.

939
01:56:02,274 --> 01:56:04,401
I mess up with your life.

940
01:56:13,753 --> 01:56:14,573
So what?

941
01:56:18,341 --> 01:56:21,335
I knew this would happen.

942
01:56:36,459 --> 01:56:38,392
Hiroko called the school.

943
01:56:39,894 --> 01:56:43,087
She said she wouldn't be back here for a while after she got out of the hospital.

944
01:56:53,946 --> 01:56:56,146
It's time for me to do something.

945
01:56:56,589 --> 01:56:58,129
Something I could do.

946
01:57:02,457 --> 01:57:12,079
I need to make a decision about Hiroko, about Shota, and about my teaching career here.

947
01:57:13,185 --> 01:57:14,198
Are you quitting?

948
01:57:14,400 --> 01:57:18,713
I don't know if I can transfer when I move next.

949
01:57:19,898 --> 01:57:23,625
If I go to Hakata, I think I'll do some cramming.

950
01:57:24,459 --> 01:57:27,106
But I need time.

951
01:57:28,171 --> 01:57:31,871
You can live alone in Hakata until then.

952
01:57:34,852 --> 01:57:39,352
I'm going to get kicked out of here one way or another.

953
01:57:41,957 --> 01:57:44,371
You doubt me?

954
01:59:34,323 --> 01:59:37,523
I let my guard down.

955
01:59:38,569 --> 01:59:39,942
What do you mean?

956
01:59:42,232 --> 01:59:48,865
I thought I'd made it this far, that I could meditate the rest of the way and still make it to the end of my life.

957
01:59:51,352 --> 01:59:54,705
I thought I'd hit something this hard.

958
01:59:56,068 --> 01:59:59,175
Atsumi,Please turn back.

959
02:00:01,471 --> 02:00:05,898
I know how far I can go on my own.

960
02:00:06,148 --> 02:00:07,455
What are you talking about?

961
02:00:08,178 --> 02:00:11,071
Why don't you just leave me alone and do that?

962
02:00:14,239 --> 02:00:16,059
You can go back to being you.

963
02:00:21,222 --> 02:00:26,197
To tell you the truth, I'm still scared.

964
02:00:28,280 --> 02:00:30,594
I'm up to you...

965
02:03:14,341 --> 02:03:14,761
Hi.

966
02:03:15,081 --> 02:03:17,901
Can you take me to Byobu...Well..Sakyobana.

967
02:03:18,630 --> 02:03:19,536
Now?

968
02:03:19,893 --> 02:03:22,013
I'm sorry.
I want to see the sunrise.

969
02:03:22,155 --> 02:03:23,735
That's the farthest east.

970
02:03:23,842 --> 02:03:24,548
No problem.

971
02:04:08,498 --> 02:04:11,518
Watch your step.
There's a precipice below.

972
02:04:11,705 --> 02:04:12,499
I know.

